get news list:
URL:/news/list?valid=[0|1|2]
METHOD:GET
PARAM:valid
PARAM VALUE:
0-无效
1-有效
2-全部
RETURN VALUE:
{
    "id":"1",
    "title":"xxxx",
    "image":"image_url",//TBD:or image in binary
    "introduce":"dfjweoff",
    "valid":1,
    "createTime":"2015-03-15 12:00:12",
    "updateTime":"2015-03-16 08:00:12"
}

+==========
get new's detail
URL:/news/detail
METHOD:GET
PARAM:id(news id)
RETURN VALUE:
{
	"id":"detailId",
	"content":"news detail content"
}
